--     A simpler bound on $\sum x_i x_{i+1}$ is obtained by noting:
--     $$ \sum_{i=1}^{100} x_i x_{i+1} \le \frac{1}{4} \left(\sum_{i=1}^{100} x_i\right)^2 = \frac{1}{4}(1)^2 = \frac{1}{4} $$
